title: DDFP 344: Greatest game & greatest movie of all time
itunes:title: DDFP 344: Greatest game & greatest movie of all time
description:
Shek (@Dameshek) is joined by Handsome Hank (@NFLUKHank) to recap NFL.com's "The Greatest Game of All Time" (9:55) -- were the Patriots/ Seahawks rightful winners? The guys then review classic movies (25:00) as producer Black Tie (@ProducerTD) reveals the winner of #DDFP bracketology. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
